<item>
            <title>[LANG-1155] Add StringUtils#unwrap</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LANG-1155</link>
                <project id="12310481" key="LANG">Commons Lang</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Proposal to add a new method namely &lt;b&gt;unwrap&lt;/b&gt; to StringUtils. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The method will be responsible for unwrapping a string token from a character (or another string token). Basically, It will be the opposite of the StringUtils.wrap() method.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Possible outcomes of the method&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-style: solid;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeHeader panelHeader&quot; style=&quot;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-style: solid;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;StringUtils.java&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
     StringUtils.unwrap(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;\&apos;abc\&apos;&quot;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;\&apos;&quot;&lt;/span&gt;)    = &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;abc&quot;&lt;/span&gt;
     StringUtils.unwrap(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;\&quot;&lt;/span&gt;abc\&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;&quot;, &quot;&lt;/span&gt;\&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;&quot;)    = &quot;&lt;/span&gt;abc&quot;
     StringUtils.unwrap(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;AABabcBAA&quot;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;AA&quot;&lt;/span&gt;)  = &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;BabcB&quot;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
